                    <a href="#" class="px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-100">Utilisateurs</a>
                    <a href="#" class="px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-100">Chiens</a>
